prompt:
Create a split architectural visualization where the top is a detailed dark-themed blueprint and the bottom is a photorealistic {argument name="building_type" default="modern single-story house"} that matches the blueprint EXACTLY.

Aspect ratio: {argument name="aspect" default="3:4"}

Composition: vertical split — top section: blueprint, bottom section: realistic render, perfect structural correspondence between both sections.

Top section — Architectural blueprint:
Style: {argument name="blueprint_style" default="dark luxury blueprint, deep navy/charcoal blue background, thin glowing beige/gold lines, slightly extruded 3D wall effect, clean modern sans-serif labels, soft ambient glow"}

Content: {argument name="rooms" default="3 bedrooms, central living room, kitchen+dining, 2 bathrooms, garage, front porch, backyard pool with deck"}
Details: furniture outlines (beds, sofa, dining table), door swings and openings, window placements, circulation paths, exact proportions and spacing.

Bottom section — Photorealistic render:
MUST MATCH THE BLUEPRINT EXACTLY — no added, removed, or shifted rooms.
Architecture style: {argument name="arch_style" default="modern house, flat layered roof, smooth concrete walls, wood panel accents, large glass windows"}
Layout mapping: {argument name="mapping_rules" default="garage on left, main entrance aligned with living room, pool in backyard matching blueprint, window placements correspond to each room"}
Environment: {argument name="environment" default="suburban neighborhood, green lawn, minimal landscaping, clean driveway, golden hour soft natural light"}
Camera: {argument name="camera" default="slightly elevated front perspective, 35mm architectural view"}

Consistency rules: room positions identical, no extra structures, doors/windows aligned logically, pool matches exactly.
Style: top = architectural visualization (dark premium), bottom = photorealistic, overall = clean high-end architectural presentation.
Negative: no mismatch between blueprint and render, no extra rooms, no fantasy elements, no unrealistic proportions.

Create a single film noir–style cinematic image divided into four horizontal panels, all depicting the same {argument name="character" default="boxer"} and the same {argument name="environment" default="boxing ring"} environment, unified by lighting, atmosphere, and narrative progression across four stages of {argument name="story" default="a fight"}.

Overall style:
{argument name="lighting_style" default="Vintage Film Noir Lighting, Low Key Lighting, Hard Shadows Lighting, Split Lighting, moody and tense atmosphere, minimal fill light, deep blacks, sharp contrast, visible film grain, slight vignetting, subtle haze in the air from sweat and dust. Industrial warehouse setting, night atmosphere, light beams cutting through darkness"}. Clean horizontal separation between panels, cinematic split-screen composition, consistent character identity across all panels.

Top panel – {argument name="panel1_label" default="ROUND 1"}, {argument name="panel1_shot" default="BIRD'S-EYE SHOT"}:
{argument name="panel1_desc" default="Bird's Eye View of the ring. Stark top-down composition, ropes forming geometric frames. Two figures circling each other. Overhead spotlight creating strong geometric shadows. Light slicing through darkness, corners fading into black."}

Second panel – {argument name="panel2_label" default="ROUND 2"}, {argument name="panel2_shot" default="SIDE CLOSE-UP SHOT"}:
{argument name="panel2_desc" default="Side-profile close-up of the main subject mid-action. Intense expression, jaw clenched. One side of the face sharply lit by a hard key light, the other completely swallowed in shadow. Split Lighting carving the facial structure in classic noir sculpting."}

Third panel – {argument name="panel3_label" default="ROUND 3"}, {argument name="panel3_shot" default="EXTREME CLOSE-UP"}:
{argument name="panel3_desc" default="Extreme Close-Up on a critical detail. Heavy shadow dominance. Light catching only key textures. Film grain pronounced. The rest of the frame nearly pure black."}

Bottom panel – {argument name="panel4_label" default="FINAL ROUND"}, {argument name="panel4_shot" default="MEDIUM WIDE BACK SHOT"}:
{argument name="panel4_desc" default="Medium Wide Shot from behind the subject. Standing alone after a decisive moment, shoulders rising with breath. Rim Lighting outlining the silhouette. Light haze in the air enhancing depth. The scene fading into darkness."}

High detail, High Quality, Photorealism Style, cinematic composition, cohesive identity across all four panels, dramatic storytelling progression within a single unified noir frame.
